biography: Amaris DiScuillo Jensen is an actress, writer, producer known for Power Rangers: Origins, Book of Mormon Videos, and other various work. Born in Japan to Anthony and Hiroko, raised in Rhode Island, and later moving to Utah, she has experienced different cultures and customs. She gained her love for performing at a young age participating in plays, band, gymnastics, and dance. She attended Mark Stolzengburg's film acting class and sparked an interest in film.
name: Amaris DiScuillo
